<subSubSection pageId="30" pageNumber="31" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="30.[189,1398,1758,1842]" box="[189,303,1758,1784]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,303,1758,1784]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,303,1758,1784]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="30.[189,1398,1758,1842]" box="[189,1398,1815,1842]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
Although 
<taxonomicName authority="Grootaert &amp; Shamshev, 2012" authorityName="Grootaert &amp; Shamshev" authorityYear="2012" box="[307,587,1816,1842]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Chersodromia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sylvicola" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[307,587,1816,1842]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Chersodromia sylvicola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[595,685,1816,1842]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
is also a yellow species that we consider belonging to the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Grootaert, Cumming &amp; Shamshev" authorityYear="2007" box="[1372,1398,1816,1842]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Chersodromia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavicaput">
<emphasis box="[1372,1398,1816,1842]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">C.</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="30.[189,1399,1862,1935]" lastBlockId="30.[189,1399,1954,2028]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
<emphasis box="[189,305,1862,1888]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">flavicaput</emphasis>
group, it is quite distinct from the three other known yellow species (
<taxonomicName authority="Grootaert &amp; Shamshev, 2012" authorityName="Grootaert &amp; Shamshev" authorityYear="2012" box="[1132,1292,1862,1888]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Chersodromia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bulohensis" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[1132,1292,1862,1888]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">C. bulohensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1300,1394,1862,1888]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Grootaert, Cumming &amp; Shamshev" authorityYear="2007" box="[189,339,1908,1935]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Chersodromia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavicaput">
<emphasis box="[189,339,1908,1935]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">C. flavicaput</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
